Peeled Garlic Market Overview
The global peeled garlic market was valued at approximately USD 6.9 billion in 2023 and is expected to reach around USD 10.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.8% during the forecast period. This market growth is largely driven by increasing consumer demand for convenience foods, health benefits associated with garlic, and the growing popularity of processed garlic products in various culinary applications.

